{"snp3.12:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 3.12 ","snp3.12:0.2":"Dvayatanupassanasutta ","snp3.12:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp3.12:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati pubbarame migaramatupasade. ","snp3.12:1.3":"Tena kho pana samayena bhagava tadahuposathe pannarase punnaya punnamaya rattiya bhikkhusanghaparivuto abbhokase nisinno hoti. ","snp3.12:1.4":"Atha kho bhagava tunhibhutam tunhibhutam bhikkhusangham anuviloketva bhikkhu amantesi: ","snp3.12:2.1":"“‘Ye te, bhikkhave, kusala dhamma ariya niyyanika sambodhagamino, tesam vo, bhikkhave, kusalanam dhammanam ariyanam niyyanikanam sambodhagaminam ka upanisa savanaya’ti, iti ce, bhikkhave, pucchitaro assu, te evamassu vacaniya: ","snp3.12:2.2":"‘yavadeva dvayatanam dhammanam yathabhutam nanaya’ti. ","snp3.12:2.3":"Kinca dvayatam vadetha? ","snp3.12:3.1":"Idam dukkham, ayam dukkhasamudayoti ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:3.2":"Ayam dukkhanirodho, ayam dukkhanirodhagamini patipadati, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:3.3":"Evam samma dvayatanupassino kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno appamattassa atapino pahitattassa viharato dvinnam phalanam annataram phalam patikankham—","snp3.12:3.4":"dittheva dhamme anna, sati va upadisese anagamita”ti. ","snp3.12:4.1":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","snp3.12:4.2":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:5.1":"“Ye dukkham nappajananti, ","snp3.12:5.2":"atho dukkhassa sambhavam; ","snp3.12:5.3":"Yattha ca sabbaso dukkham, ","snp3.12:5.4":"asesam uparujjhati; ","snp3.12:5.5":"Tanca maggam na jananti, ","snp3.12:5.6":"dukkhupasamagaminam. ","snp3.12:6.1":"Cetovimuttihina te, ","snp3.12:6.2":"Atho pannavimuttiya; ","snp3.12:6.3":"Abhabba te antakiriyaya, ","snp3.12:6.4":"Te ve jatijarupaga. ","snp3.12:7.1":"Ye ca dukkham pajananti, ","snp3.12:7.2":"atho dukkhassa sambhavam; ","snp3.12:7.3":"Yattha ca sabbaso dukkham, ","snp3.12:7.4":"asesam uparujjhati; ","snp3.12:7.5":"Tanca maggam pajananti, ","snp3.12:7.6":"dukkhupasamagaminam. ","snp3.12:8.1":"Cetovimuttisampanna, ","snp3.12:8.2":"Atho pannavimuttiya; ","snp3.12:8.3":"Bhabba te antakiriyaya, ","snp3.12:8.4":"Na te jatijarupagati. ","snp3.12:9.1":"‘Siya annenapi pariyayena samma dvayatanupassana’ti, iti ce, bhikkhave, pucchitaro assu; ","snp3.12:9.2":"‘siya’tissu vacaniya. ","snp3.12:9.3":"Kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:9.4":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam upadhipaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:9.5":"Upadhinam tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:9.6":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:9.7":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:10.1":"“Upadhinidana pabhavanti dukkha, ","snp3.12:10.2":"Ye keci lokasmimanekarupa; ","snp3.12:10.3":"Yo ve avidva upadhim karoti, ","snp3.12:10.4":"Punappunam dukkhamupeti mando; ","snp3.12:10.5":"Tasma pajanam upadhim na kayira, ","snp3.12:10.6":"Dukkhassa jatippabhavanupassiti. ","snp3.12:11.1":"‘Siya annenapi pariyayena samma dvayatanupassana’ti, iti ce, bhikkhave, pucchitaro assu; ","snp3.12:11.2":"‘siya’tissu vacaniya. ","snp3.12:11.3":"Kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:11.4":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam avijjapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:11.5":"Avijjaya tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:11.6":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:11.7":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:12.1":"“Jatimaranasamsaram, ","snp3.12:12.2":"ye vajanti punappunam; ","snp3.12:12.3":"Itthabhavannathabhavam, ","snp3.12:12.4":"avijjayeva sa gati. ","snp3.12:13.1":"Avijja hayam mahamoho, ","snp3.12:13.2":"Yenidam samsitam ciram; ","snp3.12:13.3":"Vijjagata ca ye satta, ","snp3.12:13.4":"Na te gacchanti punabbhavanti. ","snp3.12:14.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:14.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:14.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam sankharapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:14.4":"Sankharanam tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:14.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:14.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:15.1":"“Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti, ","snp3.12:15.2":"sabbam sankharapaccaya; ","snp3.12:15.3":"Sankharanam nirodhena, ","snp3.12:15.4":"natthi dukkhassa sambhavo. ","snp3.12:16.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","snp3.12:16.2":"dukkham sankharapaccaya; ","snp3.12:16.3":"Sabbasankharasamatha, ","snp3.12:16.4":"sannanam uparodhana; ","snp3.12:16.5":"Evam dukkhakkhayo hoti, ","snp3.12:16.6":"etam natva yathatatham. ","snp3.12:17.1":"Sammaddasa vedaguno, ","snp3.12:17.2":"Sammadannaya pandita; ","snp3.12:17.3":"Abhibhuyya marasamyogam, ","snp3.12:17.4":"Na gacchanti punabbhavanti. ","snp3.12:18.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:18.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:18.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam vinnanapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:18.4":"Vinnanassa tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:18.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:18.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:19.1":"“Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti, ","snp3.12:19.2":"Sabbam vinnanapaccaya; ","snp3.12:19.3":"Vinnanassa nirodhena, ","snp3.12:19.4":"Natthi dukkhassa sambhavo. ","snp3.12:20.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","snp3.12:20.2":"Dukkham vinnanapaccaya; ","snp3.12:20.3":"Vinnanupasama bhikkhu, ","snp3.12:20.4":"Nicchato parinibbutoti. ","snp3.12:21.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:21.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:21.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam phassapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:21.4":"Phassassa tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:21.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:21.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:22.1":"“Tesam phassaparetanam, ","snp3.12:22.2":"Bhavasotanusarinam; ","snp3.12:22.3":"Kummaggapatipannanam, ","snp3.12:22.4":"Ara samyojanakkhayo. ","snp3.12:23.1":"Ye ca phassam parinnaya, ","snp3.12:23.2":"Annayupasame rata; ","snp3.12:23.3":"Te ve phassabhisamaya, ","snp3.12:23.4":"Nicchata parinibbutati. ","snp3.12:24.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:24.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:24.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam vedanapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:24.4":"Vedananam tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:24.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:24.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:25.1":"“Sukham va yadi va dukkham, ","snp3.12:25.2":"Adukkhamasukham saha; ","snp3.12:25.3":"Ajjhattanca bahiddha ca, ","snp3.12:25.4":"Yam kinci atthi veditam. ","snp3.12:26.1":"Etam dukkhanti natvana, ","snp3.12:26.2":"Mosadhammam palokinam; ","snp3.12:26.3":"Phussa phussa vayam passam, ","snp3.12:26.4":"Evam tattha vijanati; ","snp3.12:26.5":"Vedananam khaya bhikkhu, ","snp3.12:26.6":"Nicchato parinibbutoti. ","snp3.12:27.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:27.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:27.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam tanhapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:27.4":"Tanhaya tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:27.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:27.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:28.1":"“Tanhadutiyo puriso, ","snp3.12:28.2":"Dighamaddhana samsaram; ","snp3.12:28.3":"Itthabhavannathabhavam, ","snp3.12:28.4":"Samsaram nativattati. ","snp3.12:29.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","snp3.12:29.2":"Tanham dukkhassa sambhavam; ","snp3.12:29.3":"Vitatanho anadano, ","snp3.12:29.4":"Sato bhikkhu paribbajeti. ","snp3.12:30.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:30.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:30.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam upadanapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:30.4":"Upadananam tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:30.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:30.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:31.1":"“Upadanapaccaya bhavo, ","snp3.12:31.2":"Bhuto dukkham nigacchati; ","snp3.12:31.3":"Jatassa maranam hoti, ","snp3.12:31.4":"Eso dukkhassa sambhavo. ","snp3.12:32.1":"Tasma upadanakkhaya, ","snp3.12:32.2":"Sammadannaya pandita; ","snp3.12:32.3":"Jatikkhayam abhinnaya, ","snp3.12:32.4":"Na gacchanti punabbhavanti. ","snp3.12:33.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:33.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:33.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam arambhapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:33.4":"Arambhanam tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:33.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:33.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:34.1":"“Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti, ","snp3.12:34.2":"Sabbam arambhapaccaya; ","snp3.12:34.3":"Arambhanam nirodhena, ","snp3.12:34.4":"Natthi dukkhassa sambhavo. ","snp3.12:35.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","snp3.12:35.2":"Dukkham arambhapaccaya; ","snp3.12:35.3":"Sabbarambham patinissajja, ","snp3.12:35.4":"Anarambhe vimuttino. ","snp3.12:36.1":"Ucchinnabhavatanhassa, ","snp3.12:36.2":"Santacittassa bhikkhuno; ","snp3.12:36.3":"Vikkhino jatisamsaro, ","snp3.12:36.4":"Natthi tassa punabbhavoti. ","snp3.12:37.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:37.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:37.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam aharapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:37.4":"Aharanam tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:37.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:37.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:38.1":"“Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti, ","snp3.12:38.2":"Sabbam aharapaccaya; ","snp3.12:38.3":"Aharanam nirodhena, ","snp3.12:38.4":"Natthi dukkhassa sambhavo. ","snp3.12:39.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","snp3.12:39.2":"Dukkham aharapaccaya; ","snp3.12:39.3":"Sabbaharam parinnaya, ","snp3.12:39.4":"Sabbaharamanissito. ","snp3.12:40.1":"Arogyam sammadannaya, ","snp3.12:40.2":"Asavanam parikkhaya; ","snp3.12:40.3":"Sankhaya sevi dhammattho, ","snp3.12:40.4":"Sankhyam nopeti vedaguti. ","snp3.12:41.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:41.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:41.3":"Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti sabbam injitapaccayati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:41.4":"Injitanam tveva asesaviraganirodha natthi dukkhassa sambhavoti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:41.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:41.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:42.1":"“Yam kinci dukkham sambhoti, ","snp3.12:42.2":"Sabbam injitapaccaya; ","snp3.12:42.3":"Injitanam nirodhena, ","snp3.12:42.4":"Natthi dukkhassa sambhavo. ","snp3.12:43.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","snp3.12:43.2":"Dukkham injitapaccaya; ","snp3.12:43.3":"Tasma hi ejam vossajja, ","snp3.12:43.4":"Sankhare uparundhiya; ","snp3.12:43.5":"Anejo anupadano, ","snp3.12:43.6":"Sato bhikkhu paribbajeti. ","snp3.12:44.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:44.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:44.3":"Nissitassa calitam hotiti, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:44.4":"Anissito na calatiti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:44.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:44.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:45.1":"“Anissito na calati, ","snp3.12:45.2":"Nissito ca upadiyam; ","snp3.12:45.3":"Itthabhavannathabhavam, ","snp3.12:45.4":"Samsaram nativattati. ","snp3.12:46.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","snp3.12:46.2":"Nissayesu mahabbhayam; ","snp3.12:46.3":"Anissito anupadano, ","snp3.12:46.4":"Sato bhikkhu paribbajeti. ","snp3.12:47.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:47.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:47.3":"Rupehi, bhikkhave, arupa santatarati, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:47.4":"Arupehi nirodho santataroti, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:47.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:47.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:48.1":"“Ye ca rupupaga satta, ","snp3.12:48.2":"Ye ca arupatthayino; ","snp3.12:48.3":"Nirodham appajananta, ","snp3.12:48.4":"Agantaro punabbhavam. ","snp3.12:49.1":"Ye ca rupe parinnaya, ","snp3.12:49.2":"Arupesu asanthita; ","snp3.12:49.3":"Nirodhe ye vimuccanti, ","snp3.12:49.4":"Te jana maccuhayinoti. ","snp3.12:50.1":"‘Siya annenapi …pe… ","snp3.12:50.2":"kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:50.3":"Yam, bhikkhave, sadevakassa lokassa samarakassa sabrahmakassa sassamanabrahmaniya pajaya sadevamanussaya idam saccanti upanijjhayitam tadamariyanam etam musati yathabhutam sammappannaya sudittham, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:50.4":"Yam, bhikkhave, sadevakassa …pe… sadevamanussaya idam musati upanijjhayitam, tadamariyanam etam saccanti yathabhutam sammappannaya sudittham, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:50.5":"Evam samma …pe… ","snp3.12:50.6":"athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:51.1":"“Anattani attamanim, ","snp3.12:51.2":"Passa lokam sadevakam; ","snp3.12:51.3":"Nivittham namarupasmim, ","snp3.12:51.4":"Idam saccanti mannati. ","snp3.12:52.1":"Yena yena hi mannanti, ","snp3.12:52.2":"Tato tam hoti annatha; ","snp3.12:52.3":"Tanhi tassa musa hoti, ","snp3.12:52.4":"Mosadhammanhi ittaram. ","snp3.12:53.1":"Amosadhammam nibbanam, ","snp3.12:53.2":"Tadariya saccato vidu; ","snp3.12:53.3":"Te ve saccabhisamaya, ","snp3.12:53.4":"Nicchata parinibbutati. ","snp3.12:54.1":"‘Siya annenapi pariyayena samma dvayatanupassana’ti, iti ce, bhikkhave, pucchitaro assu; ","snp3.12:54.2":"‘siya’tissu vacaniya. ","snp3.12:54.3":"Kathanca siya? ","snp3.12:54.4":"Yam, bhikkhave, sadevakassa lokassa samarakassa sabrahmakassa sassamanabrahmaniya pajaya sadevamanussaya idam sukhanti upanijjhayitam, tadamariyanam etam dukkhanti yathabhutam sammappannaya sudittham, ayamekanupassana. ","snp3.12:54.5":"Yam, bhikkhave, sadevakassa …pe… sadevamanussaya idam dukkhanti upanijjhayitam tadamariyanam etam sukhanti yathabhutam sammappannaya sudittham, ayam dutiyanupassana. ","snp3.12:54.6":"Evam samma dvayatanupassino kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno appamattassa atapino pahitattassa viharato dvinnam phalanam annataram phalam patikankham—","snp3.12:54.7":"dittheva dhamme anna, sati va upadisese anagamitati. ","snp3.12:54.8":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","snp3.12:54.9":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","snp3.12:55.1":"“Rupa sadda rasa gandha, ","snp3.12:55.2":"Phassa dhamma ca kevala; ","snp3.12:55.3":"Ittha kanta manapa ca, ","snp3.12:55.4":"Yavatatthiti vuccati. ","snp3.12:56.1":"Sadevakassa lokassa, ","snp3.12:56.2":"Ete vo sukhasammata; ","snp3.12:56.3":"Yattha cete nirujjhanti, ","snp3.12:56.4":"Tam nesam dukkhasammatam. ","snp3.12:57.1":"Sukhanti ditthamariyehi, ","snp3.12:57.2":"Sakkayassuparodhanam; ","snp3.12:57.3":"Paccanikamidam hoti, ","snp3.12:57.4":"Sabbalokena passatam. ","snp3.12:58.1":"Yam pare sukhato ahu, ","snp3.12:58.2":"Tadariya ahu dukkhato; ","snp3.12:58.3":"Yam pare dukkhato ahu, ","snp3.12:58.4":"Tadariya sukhato vidu. ","snp3.12:59.1":"Passa dhammam durajanam, ","snp3.12:59.2":"Sampamulhetthaviddasu; ","snp3.12:59.3":"Nivutanam tamo hoti, ","snp3.12:59.4":"Andhakaro apassatam. ","snp3.12:60.1":"Satanca vivatam hoti, ","snp3.12:60.2":"Aloko passatamiva; ","snp3.12:60.3":"Santike na vijananti, ","snp3.12:60.4":"Maga dhammassa kovida. ","snp3.12:61.1":"Bhavaragaparetehi, ","snp3.12:61.2":"Bhavasotanusaribhi; ","snp3.12:61.3":"Maradheyyanupannehi, ","snp3.12:61.4":"Nayam dhammo susambudho. ","snp3.12:62.1":"Ko nu annatra mariyehi, ","snp3.12:62.2":"Padam sambuddhumarahati; ","snp3.12:62.3":"Yam padam sammadannaya, ","snp3.12:62.4":"Parinibbanti anasava”ti. ","snp3.12:63.1":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","snp3.12:63.2":"Attamana te bhikkhu bhagavato bhasitam abhinandunti. ","snp3.12:63.3":"Imasminca pana veyyakaranasmim bhannamane satthimattanam bhikkhunam anupadaya asavehi cittani vimuccimsuti. ","snp3.12:63.4":"Dvayatanupassanasuttam dvadasamam. ","snp3.12:64.0":"Tassuddanam ","snp3.12:64.1":"Saccam upadhi avijja ca, ","snp3.12:64.2":"sankhare vinnanapancamam; ","snp3.12:64.3":"Phassavedaniya tanha, ","snp3.12:64.4":"upadanarambhaahara; ","snp3.12:64.5":"Injitam calitam rupam, ","snp3.12:64.6":"saccam dukkhena solasati. ","snp3.12:64.7":"Mahavaggo tatiyo. ","snp3.12:65.0":"Tassuddanam ","snp3.12:65.1":"Pabbajja ca padhananca, ","snp3.12:65.2":"subhasitanca sundari; ","snp3.12:65.3":"Maghasuttam sabhiyo ca, ","snp3.12:65.4":"selo sallanca vuccati. ","snp3.12:66.1":"Vasettho capi kokali, ","snp3.12:66.2":"Nalako dvayatanupassana; ","snp3.12:66.3":"Dvadasetani suttani, ","snp3.12:66.4":"Mahavaggoti vuccatiti. "}